name: Rocket AI (Oscar)
description:
This is a project by Oscar Guo made under the guidance of Coding Minds Academy! Pick a mode along with a scene and press start to explore each stage of a rudimentary rocket launch. The AI mode showcases various NN models trained using Unity ML.

Landing: the rocket must land on the platform softly (space bar)

Orienting: the rocket must orient itself (WASD) to point at the cube without spinning too fast

Traveling: the rocket must reach the target in the air before softly touching the goal
